{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"343fa5a28b","title":"湘潭专区有些农业社歧视、打击单干农民","origin":"美国图书馆收藏","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"396024a329","index":0,"year":1957,"month":4,"day":9,"articleId":"343fa5a28b"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3ab27bb9a4","name":"胡坚"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"c959c2856f","type":"title","text":"湘潭专区有些农业社歧视、打击单干农民","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"343fa5a28b"},{"id":"2c3a432b3b","type":"authors","text":"胡坚","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"343fa5a28b"},{"id":"05ebea5941","type":"paragraph","text":"新华社长沙9日讯　湖南省湘潭专区有些农业社歧视、打击单干农民的现象很严重。它们用坏田、远田换单干户的好田和近田，单干户的耕牛也由社里“统”起来。湘潭县泉塘子乡四十三户单干农民中有六户的耕牛归社控制，浏阳县有三百三十户单干户联名告农业社的状。由于以上原因，占全区总农户2．5％的单干农民生产情绪都不高，他们有80％的“板田”到现在还没有翻耕。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"343fa5a28b"},{"id":"63b81768d2","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：1957年4月9日新华通讯社编《内部参考》。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"343fa5a28b"}],"page":{"id":"051728dbf7","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"343fa5a28b","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}